borehole.gui

Class Data

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • borehole.gui.Data

  • public final class Data
extends java.util.Observable
    The data class is a storage box class that let the different threads change and retrieve the different data. The class is a subclass of the java class Observable, which allows for observers to subscribe and update their values whenever a change happens. Thread safety is achived using synchronized methods .
